    </p>
    <p class="page-design__our-experience">
        <ul class="page-design__our-experience--list">
           <li>
               <strong>Always take marked taxis -</strong> Theft is becoming an increased problem especially in tourist areas. No matter how close you are to your destination, take marked taxis, better safe than sorry.
           </li>
           <li>
               The temperature in Ecuador varies by region. Quito weather reports will say it will rain everyday and you will not be able to find a cloud in the sky. Check the region you will be visiting to determine the best time to visit. 
           </li> 
           <li>
               <strong> Bargain - </strong> This is especially true in the Galapagos when trying to find accommodations. Stick to your guns and save some money. 
           </li>   
        </ul>
    </p>
